{"tid":2077559,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[on9爛果］新系統不支援力度觸控   揭 Apple Watch Series 6 硬件變革","createTime":"2020-06-24T11:13:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T20:55:35.000Z","uid":58335,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"67485c68d8efdfd358d15432e16b26521d876fa4","tid":2077559,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T11:13:03.000Z","msg":"On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨日分享過 watchOS 7 的多項全新功能，經過一日讓開發者和傳媒「尋寶」後，卻發現新系統將一項主要功能「賜死」。Apple 在 watchOS 7 停止支援 Force Touch 力度觸控功能，並要求開發者尋求其他方案取而代之。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由於 Apple Watch 的屏幕尺寸限制，很多開發者都會利用 Force Touch 功能，透過用戶不同的觸控或按壓力度，去顯示不同介面或展示不同內容，Force Touch 是很多程式的基本操控方式之一。在全新的用戶界面指引中，Apple 明確要求開發者將長按或大力按壓以展示隱藏菜單的做法更改，應該考慮將菜單移至其他地方。<br />\n<br />\n類似的要求在之前亦曾經試過，當時 Apple 決定由 iPhone XR 開始取消支援 3D Touch 功能，而 iPhone 11 系列和全新 iPhone SE 亦沒有再支援 3D Touch。外國傳媒相信今次 watchOS 7 終止支援 Force Touch，意味著下一代 Apple Watch 的硬件會有所改變，情況就好像 iPhone XR 一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.eprice.com.hk/nb/talk/1141/27243/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.eprice.com.hk%2Fnb%2Ftalk%2F1141%2F27243%2F1%2F&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPuPMooGStKW6IyA4tNg2jBs%3D&h=af0ca136\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.eprice.com.hk/nb/talk/1141/27243/1/</a>"},{"pid":"1d53ccdee4cd7d879bbf4810becb78a886d5b75e","tid":2077559,"uid":105678,"like":9,"dislike":33,"score":-24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T11:22:31.000Z","msg":"垃圾功能，一早應該cut，apple做得好"},{"pid":"e03304dd5ccf6fffb54edfe4bb66f9a6b95fe3d7","tid":2077559,"uid":16792,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T14:50:14.000Z","msg":"個mon咁細都取消，Apple有心玩野"},{"pid":"2758e0f2823762d4e59f96cd749e9d0a4b7b709c","tid":2077559,"uid":8410,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T14:53:02.000Z","msg":"又想減少成本， 但又會加價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61fc1de7356f1e7d5991d15eb11ee47ab76f3aa4","tid":2077559,"uid":58335,